Name: Catalyst Jett
Description: Hailing from the futuristic city of Meowtronopolis, Catalyst Jett is a sleek, shiny black box-shaped being decked out with unconventional cat-button controls. With arms and legs powered by rocket thrusters, Jett zooms through the sky, performing aerobatic feats that leave audiences in awe. The screen-face of Catalyst Jett features a charming cat visage, complete with mysterious glasses that hint at a genius-level intellect behind those reflective lenses. As a prominent member of the WebtrES club, Jett is known for innovative thinking and leading the charge in digital revolutions, all while maintaining a purrfect sense of style and finesse.
